attributes.title: Haunted by TOADS and RASPBERRYS!!! 🐸🍇
attributes.review: This app is absolutely terrible. It took 9 years and 10 days to download and when it finally did I found myself cursed and haunted by toads and raspberry’s. The app itself released the toads and raspberry’s from my screen and they immediately morphed together into a giant toad shaped raspberry that likes to follow me around and haunt  me while I sleep. It literally won’t leave me alone and I’m super disappointed that this app would cause such and inconvenience. The toad-raspberry is sitting right next to me as I wright this review and it has a smug expression because it thinks it’s better than me or something. I cannot believe this. This app must be taken down before other poor souls that download it are haunted by toad-raspberrys like me. Please have mercy on us innocent people and take down this app for the safety of us all.🍇🐸🍇🥺
